instructions: On your Android phone, open Datally. Tap Daily limit . Set the amount you can use in a day. Tap Set a daily limit .

On your Android phone, open Datally. Tap Daily limit . If you want to block mobile data until the end of the day (12 a.m.), tap Block data for today . If you want to turn off Daily limit, tap Turn off daily limit .
On your Android phone, open Datally. Tap Daily limit . Tap Turn off daily limit .
